                                  (NP (NN catfish)))))

                            (NP

                                  (NP (DT the) (NN restaurant) (POS 's))
                                  (NN special))))
                            (. .)
                            (NP
                              (NP (NNP Ellen))

                                      (NP (NN fun))))))))))
                      (. .)))
                  (S
                    (NP (PRP They))
                    (VP (VBD had)
                      (NP
                        (NP (NNS lots))
                        (PP (IN of)
                          (NP (NN fun)))))
                    (. .))
                  (S
                    (NP (PRP They))
                    (VP (VBD stayed)
                      (NP (DT the) (NN night))
                      (SBAR (IN because)
                        (S
                          (NP (PRP they))
                          (VP (VBD were)
                            (ADJP (JJ tired))))))
                    (. .))

                              (NP (NN time))

    (. .)))
